<paragraph id="9979FA25FFEE933CBCCBFD7978F7FD4B" blockId="6.[151,1437,582,1795]" pageId="6" pageNumber="567">
<emphasis id="ABB22637FFEE933CBCCBFD797922FD03" bold="true" box="[199,519,654,679]" pageId="6" pageNumber="567">
Condition of the 
<typeStatus id="467D4487FFEE933CBD9BFD797927FD03" box="[407,514,654,679]" pageId="6" pageNumber="567">holotype</typeStatus>
:
</emphasis>
Glued on paper triangle; right and left flagellum lost. Right foreleg broken and stored in a microtube; foretibia and foretarsus lost; right midtarsus lost; third tarsal segment of the right hindleg lost. Right forewing mounted between coverslips. Genitalia not dissected.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="D1DCA9AEFFEE933CBCCBFD0D7EAEFCB6" box="[199,1419,762,787]" pageId="6" pageNumber="567" type="description">
